{"id":652290,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/【敏感词库】微博发布禁词：狗共/","date":"2020-08-09T12:48:29Z","modified":"2020-08-09T12:48:29Z","title":"【敏感词库】微博发布禁词：狗共","content":"<p>8月8日，有网友发现在新浪微博上一段正常的“救助弃犬”的信息无法正常发出，经测试发现禁发敏感词为“狗共”，而这段信息中“狗共”实为“狗,共”，完全是网友消息的无意触发。该词是如何被纳入了“新浪微博禁发词库”，令人产生诸多联想。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652292\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/Ee5IPokUYAAz6XN.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/Ee5IPokUYAAz6XN.jpeg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/Ee5IPokUYAAz6XN-169x300.jpeg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/Ee5IPokUYAAz6XN-576x1024.jpeg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>被标点符号所隔开的内容并不影响“审查AI”的前后文识别，相关情况以前就有发生：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"njwUIptct1\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91dada%e4%b8%8e%e9%94%a6%e6%8b%bc/\">【敏感词库】“dada”与“锦拼”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"《【敏感词库】“dada”与“锦拼”》—中国数字时代\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91dada%e4%b8%8e%e9%94%a6%e6%8b%bc/embed/#?secret=njwUIptct1\" data-secret=\"njwUIptct1\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,38827,38912,16848],"tags":[9113,9283,8859,41436,19622]}